peru's consuemr price index rose 5.3 pctlast month to 13,914.4 (base 100) following a 5.3 pct increasein february and 5.3 pct rise in march 1986, the nationalstatistics institute said.    It said that the accumulated inflation for the first threemonths of 1987 was 18.5 pct compared to 15.4 pct for the sameperiod last year.    Inflation for the 12-month period ending march 1987 was67.4 pct compared to 120.8 pct for the 12-month period endingmarch 1986. Reuter&#3;